Action.author: jyellick
Action.body: The underlying cause here has to do with map serialization not being deterministic. It so happens that we've only ever really used a single value in this map, so it's never surfaced before. I have what I believe is a workaround, but it will require an update to the vendored protobuf, investigating.

Action.author: jyellick
Action.body: Since this cannot be fixed without proto v1.1.0, and that change is too large to contain for v1.2, I've pushed the fix version out to v1.3.
